### Create a new person
POST http://localhost:8080/persons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "1",
  "name": "Alice",
  "age": 30
}

### Get person by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/persons/1

### Update person by ID
PUT http://localhost:8080/persons/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Alice Updated",
  "age": 31
}

### Get person again to check update
GET http://localhost:8080/persons/1

### Delete person by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/persons/1

